Package: cc
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), tmux (>= 3.0), cron
Recommends: claude-code
Maintainer: Robin <robin@nurrobin.de>
Homepage: https://github.com/robinr2/cc
Description: Claude Code tmux session manager
 Manages Claude Code sessions inside tmux with descriptions,
 fuzzy attach, scheduled cron jobs, and built-in tmux defaults
 for mouse scrolling, truecolor, and large scrollback buffers.
